            "$LINK": {
              "type": "pricing",
              "path": "/chime/chime-sdk/pricing/"
            }
          },
          "bodyText": "WebRTC media sessions are billed per minute for each “attendee” (i.e. an instance of your application) while connected to the session, regardless of which media modalities (screen share, screen view, two-way audio, one-way audio, two-way video, or one-way video) are used.",
