              "type": "pricing",
              "path": "/chime/chime-sdk/pricing/"
            }
          },
          "bodyText": "Media replication is billed minute for each destination WebRTC media sessions, regardless of the number attendees connected to the session. Media replication is billed in addition to the attendee minutes billed for attendees connected to both the destination WebRTC media sessions.",
